    Library RTN_MenuSync_1_0_0

    Namespace: http://www.modeldev.restauranttechnologynetwork.com/models/v1

    • BusinessObjects 
      Name Description
      MenuItem
      A single item within a menu product. A menu item may have multiple copies to support dynamic pricing (or multiple prices per menu item) based on capabilities of publisher / subscriber systems, though the pricing data structure supports multiple/intelligent/dynamic pricing.
      Menu
      A collection of MenuItems, MenuProducts, Ingredients, Modifiers, and Prices.
      Modifier  
      MenuProduct
      A group of one or more menu items, typically sold with a single price.
      RestaurantDetails
      Specifies the location and menu details for a restaurant.
    • CoreObjects 
      Name Description
      BaselineNutrition
      Basic nutrition information.
      DietaryRestrictions
      Provides information regarding dietary restrictions.
      ServingSize
      Specifies the details related to the size of the portion.
      Default
      A preselected group of items associated with an item.
      Channel
      Identifies a channel and description information.
      AllergenDetails
      Specifies whether an item contains or is free from an allergen.
